{"tid":55753,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"一首歌既Credit應該比邊個?","createTime":"2016-12-26T15:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T02:28:03.000Z","uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b258ca75cd9eca1255a1bba14f37e4c4df9d4d","tid":55753,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"成日見有人話邊個邊個歌手D詞好有深度, 邊幾句好好聽<br />\n但明明就唔係果個歌手作詞作曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f16a56a4c5e5d49005ed31f19fb341255468e3","tid":55753,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"我就覺得係曲同編"},{"pid":"382312cd7073ec7616f24f1615f1095255473e56","tid":55753,"uid":365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"作曲"},{"pid":"a3fcc2ca5747fe84f97679f070edebbc187d93f8","tid":55753,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"監製"},{"pid":"0b400568482db969d0c76fa6d07f5588b60d9746","tid":55753,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:47:55.000Z","msg":"曲producer <br />\n多數呢兩位都搞埋編曲"},{"pid":"ccd11caf05413c8d158421f8ad56a94f737c7800","tid":55753,"uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:26:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得最重要是唱片/歌曲監製，因為一首歌能唔能夠出現，係由佢地決定。<br />\n至於首歌的 credit，我覺得係成 team 人的功勞，監、唱、曲、編及詞也重要。<br />\n比較多人講歌詞，是因為歌詞可以寫出來，比較實在。<br />\n但如果首歌唱得難聽，曲及編曲又難聽，咁我都唔會聽，更加唔會去留意歌詞。"},{"pid":"2832b393aba9ecabf79c4050801d6d1e364ef9b4","tid":55753,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得最重要是唱片/歌曲監製，因為一首歌能唔能夠出現，係由佢地決定。<br />\n至於首歌的 credit，我覺得係成 team 人的功勞，監、唱、曲、編及詞也重要。<br />\n比較多人講歌詞，是因為歌詞可以寫出來，比較實在。<br />\n但如果首歌唱得難聽，曲及編曲又難聽，咁我都唔會聽，更加唔會去留意歌詞。</blockquote><br />\n最尾個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2d455fef29de4a00a1a456f14fee011510bca1","tid":55753,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"睇咩歌<br />\n<br />\n有D詞好有深度 但旋律麻麻<br />\n<br />\n有D旋律好聽 詞就唔多掂"},{"pid":"520990316394d35ecdd42c17fcdccdc4552667b9","tid":55753,"uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-07T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"睇完叱吒先知一首歌的credit 要比埋A&amp;R同監製"},{"pid":"92ea7ab625218b0a79843d30d4c2301ad0077157","tid":55753,"uid":73180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-07T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"作曲果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過宜家淨係作曲會無飯食<br />\n通常都會編埋做埋監製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beba40ac830679b647114f2d90a12670a3ccf15b","tid":55753,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-07T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"曲真係唔識評論好唔好"}]}